    "##  Converting Date to Ordinal\n",
    "\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 11,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import datetime as dt \n",
    "\n",
    "df_india[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(df_india[\"date\"]) \n",
    "df_india[\"date\"] = df_india[\"date\"].map(dt.datetime.toordinal) "
   ]
